{"tid":1668801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[有個眾籌諗法] 資助餐廳安裝Now/I-Cable 新聞台","createTime":"2019-10-22T07:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T16:06:36.000Z","uid":166601,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c0a21c3d1b8ff91dbe8ad50d082be8f8f418f89d","tid":1668801,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"如題，小弟有依個想法一段時間，點解會有藍絲出現? 其實好大程度上係佢地日常接觸嘅新聞有關，例如TVB 經常偏頗報導新聞，令到冇選擇嘅大眾相信TVB嘅報導，大家可能會話咁可以睇Facebook: 一定年紀嘅人未必識用or 會睇Facebook or 其他media。<br />\n<br />\n所以我<span style=\"color: green;\">建議可以資助全港有意參與計劃嘅餐廳去安裝Now/I-cable 新聞台</span>，令食客或公眾接收多角度資訊。 <br />\n<br />\n依個建議係初步階段，如果大家<br />\n認同依個想法可以<span style=\"color: gold;\">投個贊成</span><br />\n唔認同/有更好嘅方法<span style=\"color: blue;\">投個反對</span> &ndash; 再係下面俾個意見去改善<br />\n<br />\n如果投票總數量 <span style=\"color: green;\">大於 4000(數字參照近期熱門Post)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">下一步:</span><br />\n會再開Post 尋找志願者 組成一team 人去發起及執行眾籌計劃"},{"pid":"62ef06ba36c76933ab4e4fc1a04c64409bbb2121","tid":1668801,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:54:31.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"2b1f5e80ed29e7c4691aea99dc6c4dbd08de514d","tid":1668801,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"54e10479b98f4cfc4a3a86d4d8cde9e359de20dd","tid":1668801,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"0dcdf69bc5cda4e584aafb02a9c554912cf6f839","tid":1668801,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"9b16fe23584ec4051ffaec145c94c1550b02e86a","tid":1668801,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:55:13.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"fae2d2d25486d1f265ca98a21f35ada5c879cf1c","tid":1668801,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:55:27.000Z","